{"id":55999,"title":"Congenital glaucoma in Wagner syndrome.","abstract":"Wagner syndrome is a rare inherited vitreoretinopathy. We describe 3 related patients with Wagner syndrome who presented with congenital glaucoma at age 3 months and required multiple surgical interventions to control their intraocular pressure. All experienced visual loss and glaucomatous optic neuropathy. ","date":"2014-06-13","categories":"Eye Diseases","split":"test","url":"http://www.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/pubmed/24767812","annotations":[{"name":"Glaucoma","weight":0.872951,"wikipedia_article":"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Glaucoma"},{"name":"Heredity","weight":0.813916,"wikipedia_article":"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Heredity"},{"name":"Vision loss","weight":0.801843,"wikipedia_article":"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Vision_loss"},{"name":"Congenital disorder","weight":0.801318,"wikipedia_article":"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Congenital_disorder"},{"name":"Intraocular pressure","weight":0.792838,"wikipedia_article":"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Intraocular_pressure"},{"name":"Surgery","weight":0.689634,"wikipedia_article":"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Surgery"},{"name":"Human eye","weight":0.634937,"wikipedia_article":"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Human_eye"},{"name":"Syndrome","weight":0.624832,"wikipedia_article":"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Syndrome"},{"name":"Peripheral neuropathy","weight":0.526043,"wikipedia_article":"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Peripheral_neuropathy"},{"name":"Visual system","weight":0.224455,"wikipedia_article":"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Visual_system"},{"name":"Pressure","weight":0.0532834,"wikipedia_article":"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Pressure"},{"name":"Richard Wagner","weight":0.0168623,"wikipedia_article":"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Richard_Wagner"},{"name":"Optic neuropathy","weight":0.0163827,"wikipedia_article":"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Optic_neuropathy"}]}
